  },
  "name": "Chat with OpenAIs GPT via a simple Telegram Bot",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from enescingoz/awesome-n8n-templates: Chat with OpenAIs GPT via a simple Telegram Bot",
  "category": "AI",
  "tags": [
    "Telegram",
